2012;;40 Days and Nights;;American;;Peter Geiger;;Monica Keena, Christianna Carmine, Emily Sandifer, Alex Carter;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/40_Days_and_Nights;;When a massive tectonic shift triggers a tsunami capable of swallowing whole continents, the military creates an ark capable of holding only 50,000 people and the DNA of every species possible while the storm consumes most of the world.